pers=C3=B6nlichen Trainingsplan zu erhalten.</p>
    </header>

    <div class=3D"form-group">
      <label class=3D"field-label" for=3D"regName" data-i18n=3D"reg.name
">Name</label>
      <input type=3D"text" id=3D"regName" data-i18n-ph=3D"reg.namePh"
placeholder=3D"Dein Name" autocomplete=3D"off">
    </div>

    <div class=3D"form-group">
      <label class=3D"field-label" for=3D"regDob"
data-i18n=3D"reg.dob">Geburtsdatum</label>
      <input type=3D"date" id=3D"regDob" max=3D"2025-12-31" min=3D"1930-01-=
01">
      <div class=3D"hint" data-i18n=3D"reg.dobHint">Wird genutzt, um dein
Training altersgerecht anzupassen.</div>
    </div>

    <div class=3D"form-group">
      <label class=3D"field-label" for=3D"regPosition"
data-i18n=3D"reg.pos">Position im Spiel</label>
      <select id=3D"regPosition"></select>
      <div class=3D"hint" data-i18n=3D"reg.posHint">W=C3=A4hle deine genaue=
 Position
=E2=80=93 die =C3=9Cbungen und Hinweise werden darauf abgestimmt.</div>
    </div>

    <div class=3D"form-group">
      <label class=3D"field-label" data-i18n=3D"reg.lang">Sprache der Websi=
te /
Website language</label>
      <div class=3D"lang-row">
        <button type=3D"button" class=3D"lang-chip" data-lang=3D"de"
onclick=3D"setLang('de')">=F0=9F=87=A9=F0=9F=87=AA Deutsch</button>
        <button type=3D"button" class=3D"lang-chip" data-lang=3D"en"
onclick=3D"setLang('en')">=F0=9F=87=AC=F0=9F=87=A7 English</button>
